### Purpose
Tests symlink behavior through a real FUSE mount. All tests `<!-- trace: skipped -->` for syscall-boundary reasons; library semantics are traced in `test_symlinks.py.engspec`.

### Implementation Notes

```python
import errno
import os
import pytest

# mount fixture defined in test_fuse_basic or shared conftest.
pytestmark = pytest.mark.fuse
```

